      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im working on a screenplay for a gritty crime thriller. i need to set the scene for a neighborhood that feels really dangerous and rundown. can you write a paragraph describing a street in this area? i want it to feel heavy with tension and show like, the underlying social decay and the kind of places where you'd definitely watch your back. make it super vivid.",
